Rating: 3
Way too tart with the given proportion of lemon to broth. Had to add twice as much broth to reduce the pucker. Given that there is probably some variability in tartness of lemons, I will next time reduce the broth, then add the lemon a spoonful at a time. I also used a little flour to thicken the sauce. Overall a nice, simple recipe that could be used with a variety of meats and cuts.

